name: r-perm
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.0-0.2" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-perm
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/perm_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/perm/perm_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 729294987bb0f367c67c4bf4071464e097ec9a2bbdb2c63f19ebfb907c604aa0

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
    - cross-r-base {{ r_base }}    # [build_platform != target_platform]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('perm')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('perm')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=perm
  license: GPL-2.0-or-later
  summary: Perform Exact or Asymptotic permutation tests [see Fay and Shaw <doi:10.18637/jss.v036.i02>].
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
